    },
    {
      "term": "Cha hai (Fairness pitcher)",
      "definition": "An intermediate pouring vessel used in Gongfu Cha. The full brewed infusion is poured into the cha hai before being distributed to individual cups, ensuring all guests receive tea of identical strength."
