          "type": "image",
          "url": "PLACEHOLDER",
          "altText": "IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: Side-by-side comparison photograph of Camellia sinensis var. sinensis (small, narrow, dark-green leaf) and var. assamica (large, broad, lighter-green leaf), shown at actual relative sizes with labels identifying each variety, country of typical cultivation, and one flavour descriptor."
